#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.divide.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.divide"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:1 of
msgid "Divide arguments element-wise."
msgstr "逐元素地将参数相除。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:3 of
msgid "Dividend tensor."
msgstr "被除数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:5 of
msgid "Divisor tensor."
msgstr "除数张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:7 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于保存结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的数组。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:12 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:17 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The quotient `x1/x2`, element-wise. Returns a scalar if both "
"`x1` and `x2` are scalars."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 逐元素的商 `x1/x2`。如果 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是标量，则返回一个标量"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:22 of
msgid "Equivalent to `x1` / `x2` in terms of array-broadcasting."
msgstr "在数组广播方面等价于 `x1` / `x2`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:24 of
msgid "Behavior on division by zero can be changed using `seterr`."
msgstr "使用 `seterr` 可以更改除以零时的行为。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:26 of
msgid ""
"In Python 2, when both `x1` and `x2` are of an integer type, `divide` "
"will behave like `floor_divide`. In Python 3, it behaves like "
"`true_divide`."
msgstr ""
"在 Python 2 中，当 `x1` 和 `x2` 都是整数类型时，`divide` 的行为类似于 `"
"floor_divide`。在 Python 3 中，它的行为类似于 `true_divide`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.divide.divide:30 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

